"{\"uid\": \"salon.com-2024-07-27-chef-kvin-dandrea-on-top-chef-friendships-must-have-ingredients-and-the-summer-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Much like working as a chef in any restaurant kitchen, no matter the caliber or cuisine,\\\"Top Chef\\\"can be a particularly unique and rigorous experience.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 151, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In many cases, a general sense of grit and toughness is the norm, oftentimes calcified after years and years of tense kitchen interactions, incredibly frenzied cooking, frantic moments and immense stressors.\", \"from\": 152, \"to\": 359, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is often shown throughout\\\"Top Chef,\\\" too, particularly during certain challenges, likeRestaurant Wars\\u00c2\\u00a0or the Mise en Place Race, as well as any moment of the finale cook.\", \"from\": 361, \"to\": 537, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Related  For Chef Kevin D'Andrea, though, he added a certainje ne sais quoi, if you will \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 nodding to his birthplace \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 oftentimes contributing a sense of levity, a bright smile, a wink and a nod.\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 738, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In both the competition proper and also Last Chance Kitchen, D'Andrea was consistent a bright spot, often adding humor and lightness in a competition show that often times finds itself lacking such ebullience.\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 948, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition, he made some pretty stupendous dishes, too, combining his culinary background and expertise with his previous experiences on \\\"Top Chef France\\\" to make him quite the well-rounded cheftestant.\", \"from\": 949, \"to\": 1152, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Bravo and NBCU must have also been a fan of this energy and have since capitalized on D'Andrea's French heritage, culinary knowledge and on-camera charisma in order to highlight the many athletes competing in the Summer Olympics in Paris: a new Peacock show called \\\"Breaking Baguettes,\\\" hosted by\\u00c2\\u00a0D'Andrea.\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1461, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1164, \"end\": 1168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBCU\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}, {\"begin\": 1251, \"end\": 1257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9994325051903331, \"rank\": 0.0005676965019420124, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1386, \"end\": 1391, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4066613835914325e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As per Eric Goodman withNBC Olympics, \\\"Top Chef\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s charming, whisk-wielding, sports-crazed French cuisine master is inviting U.S. Olympians into his kitchen to get a front row seat to the food of his home nation, France, in the brand new series 'Breaking Baguettes.'\\\"\", \"from\": 1463, \"to\": 1731, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1555, \"end\": 1569, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_cuisine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French cuisine\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_cuisine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_cuisine\"}, {\"begin\": 1677, \"end\": 1683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999998392177205, \"rank\": 1.570121929400278e-07, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With a fun title clearly a nod to the custom of \\\"breaking bread,\\\" the show slight subverts the custom: As Goodman says, \\\"Inside each [baguette] is a hidden slip of paper \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 fortune cookie style \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 with a spicy question for either Chef Kevin or one of his special guests.\\\"\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 2006, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can tune into \\\"Breaking Baguettes\\\" now on Peacock or on the NBC Sports YouTube channel.\", \"from\": 2007, \"to\": 2098, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2071, \"end\": 2081, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9999999999690772, \"rank\": 3.0509526629767184e-11, \"text\": \"NBC Sports\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}, {\"begin\": 2082, \"end\": 2089, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.0429546395135e-14, \"text\": \"YouTube\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Salon Food recently spoke with Chef D'Andrea about his experience on \\\"Top Chef,\\\" his close-knit friendship with fellow competitor Chef Manny Barella, \\\"Breaking Baguettes\\\" and much more.\", \"from\": 2100, \"to\": 2285, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2100, \"end\": 2105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salon.com\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.4231563385850236e-27, \"text\": \"Salon\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salon.com\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salon.com\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kevin D\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099Andrea on \\\"Top Chef\\\" (Stephanie Diani/Bravo)  The following interview has been lightly edited for clarity and length.\", \"from\": 2287, \"to\": 2414, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2319, \"end\": 2328, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_Scully\", \"score\": 0.9997359323007776, \"rank\": 0.0002639424317554155, \"text\": \"Stephanie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_Scully\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_Scully\"}, {\"begin\": 2335, \"end\": 2340, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CTV_Drama_Channel\", \"score\": 0.9999999617202783, \"rank\": 3.828006597021302e-08, \"text\": \"Bravo\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CTV_Drama_Channel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CTV_Drama_Channel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hi!\", \"from\": 2416, \"to\": 2419, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Did you do any sort of special preparations for \\\"Top Chef?\\\"\", \"from\": 2420, \"to\": 2479, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"How did your previous \\\"Top Chef\\\" experience aid in your experience?\\u00c2  Yes, absolutely!\", \"from\": 2480, \"to\": 2566, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I worked on training myself within the time limits and I also watched other seasons.\", \"from\": 2567, \"to\": 2651, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As a finalist on Top Chef France, I also was in the unique position to be able to pull from past experience.\", \"from\": 2652, \"to\": 2760, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2669, \"end\": 2677, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Top_Chef\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.957328692352395e-56, \"text\": \"Top Chef\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Top_Chef\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Top_Chef\"}, {\"begin\": 2678, \"end\": 2684, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999998392177205, \"rank\": 1.570121929400278e-07, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What would you say is your favorite or best moment of the competition?\", \"from\": 2762, \"to\": 2832, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Definitely my birthday!\", \"from\": 2834, \"to\": 2857, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It came around while filming and Manny Barella organized a big surprise dinner with the whole family.\", \"from\": 2858, \"to\": 2959, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a magical moment.\", \"from\": 2960, \"to\": 2984, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Was there anything about competing on the show that you did not anticipate?\", \"from\": 2986, \"to\": 3061, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Either from the competition standpoint itself, from the television perspective, or perhaps even from watching yourself back after months have passed?\\u00c2  Being in the unique position to have competed on Top Chef internationally, I was likely the most prepared for the style of the show and for watching myself back.\", \"from\": 3062, \"to\": 3375, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s always a little out of body to see yourself on screen, but the experience is unlike anything else.\\u00c2  Lots of credit goes to the \\\"Top Chef\\\" team who made us feel comfortable and safe through the duration of filming.\", \"from\": 3376, \"to\": 3597, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kevin D'Andrea on \\\"Top Chef\\\" (David Moir/Bravo)Did you have a favorite challenge?\", \"from\": 3599, \"to\": 3680, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Conversely, was there a challenge you really didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t enjoy?\\u00c2  I really enjoyed the chaos challenge \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 that was my favorite!\", \"from\": 3681, \"to\": 3806, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There wasn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t a challenge I specifically didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t enjoy.\", \"from\": 3807, \"to\": 3864, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even when I was eliminated, I was proud to be leaving after making some of the best risotto they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d experienced on the show.\", \"from\": 3865, \"to\": 3990, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Which dish were you proudest of?\", \"from\": 3992, \"to\": 4024, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In Madison, I made a warm praline chocolate mousse for the duality challenge that I was really proud of.\", \"from\": 4026, \"to\": 4130, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4029, \"end\": 4036, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Madison\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.061399563874671e-25, \"text\": \"Madison\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Madison\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Madison\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I had a great feeling about that dish and the feedback from the judges, including Dominique Crenn who was a judge when I came in second on Top Chef France, was really positive.\\u00c2  What was the critique you received during the show that you learned the most from?\\u00c2  \\\"Top Chef\\\" gives you the once-in-a-lifetime opportunity to receive input, advice and support from the judges and renowned chefs.\", \"from\": 4131, \"to\": 4523, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4213, \"end\": 4228, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dominique_Crenn\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dominique Crenn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dominique_Crenn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dominique_Crenn\"}, {\"begin\": 4270, \"end\": 4278, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Top_Chef\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.957328692352395e-56, \"text\": \"Top Chef\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Top_Chef\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Top_Chef\"}, {\"begin\": 4279, \"end\": 4285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999998392177205, \"rank\": 1.570121929400278e-07, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I tried to take each bit of helpful critique to heart.\\u00c2  Laura Ozyilmaz and Kevin D\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099Andrea on \\\"Top Chef\\\" (David Moir/Bravo)  Do you have a number-one favorite ingredient to work with?\\u00c2  I cannot exist without garlic and fresh herbs.\", \"from\": 4524, \"to\": 4758, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4581, \"end\": 4586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\", \"score\": 0.9922634773134265, \"rank\": 0.007796842191874528, \"text\": \"Laura\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\"}, {\"begin\": 4643, \"end\": 4648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CTV_Drama_Channel\", \"score\": 0.9999999617202783, \"rank\": 3.828006597021302e-08, \"text\": \"Bravo\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CTV_Drama_Channel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CTV_Drama_Channel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What stands out for you as a formative moment that got you into cooking or food at large?\\u00c2  When I went to culinary school at 16, my professor, Mr. Troin believed in me, and he was the only one.\", \"from\": 4760, \"to\": 4954, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Most people, including myself, considered me a lost cause \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 bad at school and completely lost.\", \"from\": 4955, \"to\": 5051, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr. Troin helped me understand the love of cooking and the appreciation for focusing on something to become someone in life.\", \"from\": 5052, \"to\": 5176, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Congratulations on \\\"Breaking Baguettes\\\" (love the name, by the way!)\", \"from\": 5178, \"to\": 5246, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"How did the show come about?\\u00c2  Thank you!\", \"from\": 5247, \"to\": 5288, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Breaking Baguettes is so much fun!\", \"from\": 5289, \"to\": 5323, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am a huge fan of sports and especially the Olympics.\", \"from\": 5324, \"to\": 5378, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When NBC contacted me about doing this amazing series for the Summer Olympics, I couldn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t say \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cyes\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d fast enough.\\u00c2  Tell me a bit about Foliepops?\", \"from\": 5379, \"to\": 5530, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5384, \"end\": 5387, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.451104082379023e-16, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Foliepop's is a French patisserie located in Austin, Texas where we make delicious pastries \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 particularly the Tartelette.\", \"from\": 5532, \"to\": 5656, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5548, \"end\": 5554, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9994325051903331, \"rank\": 0.0005676965019420124, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 5577, \"end\": 5590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Circuit_of_the_Americas\", \"score\": 0.9999997186742289, \"rank\": 2.62201748493249e-07, \"text\": \"Austin, Texas\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Circuit_of_the_Americas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Circuit_of_the_Americas\"}, {\"begin\": 5577, \"end\": 5590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Circuit_of_the_Americas\", \"score\": 0.9999997186742289, \"rank\": 2.62201748493249e-07, \"text\": \"Austin, Texas\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Circuit_of_the_Americas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Circuit_of_the_Americas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Foliepop\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Tartelettes are shortbread cookies with creamy fillings and topped with milk, dark or white chocolate.\", \"from\": 5657, \"to\": 5772, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They come in a variety of decadent flavors like: chocolate, lemon, raspberry, peanut, caramel and chai.\", \"from\": 5773, \"to\": 5876, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Right now, the Foliepop\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Tartelettes are available in HEB stores across Central Texas and our goal is to make the Tartelettes available nationwide!\\u00c2  Manuel \\\"Manny\\\" Barella Lopez, Kevin D'Andrea and Tom Colicchio on \\\"Top Chef\\\" (David Moir/Bravo)  I am always a sucker for a \\\"Top Chef\\\" friendship and I thought the fun bond you had with Manny was so great and brought such levity to the show.\", \"from\": 5877, \"to\": 6271, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5934, \"end\": 5937, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H-E-B\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"HEB\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H-E-B\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H-E-B\"}, {\"begin\": 6079, \"end\": 6092, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Colicchio\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Colicchio\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Colicchio\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Colicchio\"}, {\"begin\": 6119, \"end\": 6124, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CTV_Drama_Channel\", \"score\": 0.9999999617202783, \"rank\": 3.828006597021302e-08, \"text\": \"Bravo\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CTV_Drama_Channel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CTV_Drama_Channel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What do you think helped the two of you to connect?\", \"from\": 6272, \"to\": 6323, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Manny is more than a friend \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 he became family.\", \"from\": 6325, \"to\": 6374, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, I just went to Denver to celebrate his wedding!\", \"from\": 6375, \"to\": 6431, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6399, \"end\": 6405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denver\", \"score\": 0.9999999997626219, \"rank\": 2.376003252828191e-10, \"text\": \"Denver\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denver\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denver\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When we walked in for the very first episode, Manny was just in front of me in the line to head in.\", \"from\": 6432, \"to\": 6531, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We needed to be quiet, but he had his hands behind his back, so I high fived him.\", \"from\": 6532, \"to\": 6613, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When I did, he turned around and smiled.\", \"from\": 6614, \"to\": 6654, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I winked back and it was instant friendship.\", \"from\": 6655, \"to\": 6699, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As we continued to get to know each other, we discovered that we\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d been through a lot of similar experiences, including immigrating to the U.S. and working our way up.\\u00c2  What\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s next for you?\", \"from\": 6700, \"to\": 6894, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am heading home to Paris for the Olympics where some exciting things are in the works!\", \"from\": 6896, \"to\": 6984, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6917, \"end\": 6922, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4066613835914325e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hope to share more on that, soon!\", \"from\": 6985, \"to\": 7018, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And, I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m looking forward to growing the presence and availability of Foliepop\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Tartelettes nationwide.\", \"from\": 7020, \"to\": 7127, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read more  about this topic  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2026 Salon.com, LLC.\", \"from\": 7129, \"to\": 7191, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7187, \"end\": 7190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\", \"score\": 0.9999999971369107, \"rank\": 2.863382221408765e-09, \"text\": \"LLC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reproduction of material from any Salon pages without written permission is strictly prohibited.\", \"from\": 7192, \"to\": 7288, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7226, \"end\": 7231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salon.com\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.4231563385850236e-27, \"text\": \"Salon\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salon.com\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salon.com\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SALON \\u00c2\\u00ae is registered in the U.S. Patent and Trademark Office as a trademark of Salon.com, LLC.\", \"from\": 7289, \"to\": 7385, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7370, \"end\": 7379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salon.com\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Salon.com\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salon.com\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salon.com\"}, {\"begin\": 7381, \"end\": 7384, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\", \"score\": 0.9999999971369107, \"rank\": 2.863382221408765e-09, \"text\": \"LLC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http: